==English==
=== Etymology ===
From Persian ''p&aelig;'' meaning "leg" and ''jama'' meaning "clothing".

===Noun===
'''pajamas''' ''plural''
#[[Clothes]] for wearing to bed and sleeping in, usually consisting of a loose-fitting shirt and pants.

